title: Front-end Design
content:
Use front-end languages, technology, frameworks to
creating & maintaining visually appealing and user-

title: Data Analytics
content:
Knowledgeable in SQL, Python, and TensorFlow.
Capable of working with large datasets and providing
valuable insights through data analysis. Collecting,
transforming, and organizing data from various
sources to draw insights, create data visualizations to
help businesses make informed decisions.

title: Cuteness Qualities
content:
Acting in a cute way, using my personality traits and
body language to project a sweet, innocent, and
friendly image. I can give compliments, cheer up others and company to others.

title: Psychological Counselling
content:
Have been trained in the relevant knowledge, can
Help people prevent and alleviate distress and
maladjustment, resolve crises, and increase their
ability to function better in their lives. Focus on crisis
intervention, assessment, prevention, education,
research & advocacy.
